OL,3,CLeading conservationist slams zoos for
OL,4,Ckeeping animals in captivity
OL,6,FLeading conservationist Damian
OL,7,FAspinall says there is "no
OL,8,Fjustification at all to keep animals
OL,9,Fin captivity".
OL,11,FHe is Chair of the Aspinall
OL,12,FFoundation, a global charity founded
OL,13,Fby his father John to protect
OL,14,Fendangered species.
OL,16,FDamian explains: "I think it's a very
OL,17,Fsad experience that any animal today
OL,18,Fis in captivity, we have to look back
OL,19,Fover the last 30 to 40 years and
OL,20,Funderstand that it's been a terrible
OL,21,Fmistake.
