OL,3,CLeading conservationist slams zoos for
OL,4,Ckeeping animals in captivity
OL,6,F"If you look at the 5,500 species in
OL,7,Fzoos, 95% are not critically
OL,8,Fendangered so why are they there?
OL,10,F"Then if you look at the critically
OL,11,Fendangered species, there's 45 of them
OL,12,Fand only four are viable. The rest of
OL,13,Fthem are diseased, hybridised or
OL,14,Fgenetically bottlenecked."
OL,16,FDamian was speaking following an ITV
OL,17,FNews investigation into Jersey Zoo
OL,18,Fthat .
