OL,3,CLeading conservationist slams zoos for
OL,4,Ckeeping animals in captivity
OL,6,FFormer senior staff members claim that
OL,7,Fthe charity has moved away from its
OL,8,Ffounder Gerald Durrell's vision of
OL,9,Fsaving endangered animals.
OL,11,FDamian adds: "I urge all zoos to be
OL,12,Fhonest with the public and if they're
OL,13,Fnot doing conservation work then just
OL,14,Fbe honest and say, 'look, we're a
OL,15,Fsanctuary for animals, there's no
OL,16,Fconservation value', or 'we're a
OL,17,Fbusiness and we're here to put animals
OL,18,Fin captivity open to the public', but
OL,19,Fto mislead the public that they're
OL,20,Fdoing great conservation work is
OL,21,Fsimply not true."
