OL,3,CLeading conservationist slams zoos for
OL,4,Ckeeping animals in captivity
OL,6,F"It's not just a question of the
OL,7,FDurrell Zoo now no longer interested
OL,8,Fin conservation, I think it's very
OL,9,Fhard to justify that there's any
OL,10,Fconservation value in any zoo."
OL,12,FIn response, Dr Mike Hudson, a
OL,13,FDirector at Durrell Wildlife
OL,14,FConservation Trust, says: "50% of the
OL,15,Fspecies at Jersey Zoo are classified
OL,16,Fas globally threatened by the
OL,17,FInternational Union for the
OL,18,FConservation of Nature (IUCN) in
OL,19,Fupdated figures as of April 2024."
