OL,4,Ckeeping animals in captivity
OL,6,FGlobally threatened species are
OL,7,Fcategorised as critically endangered,
OL,8,Fendangered or vulnerable to extinction
OL,9,Fon the IUCN red list.
OL,11,FDurrell also works globally to protect
OL,12,Fspecies and their habitats, such as
OL,13,Fblack lion tamarins.
OL,15,FFewer than 2,000 can be found in the
OL,16,Fwild so they are building a 'safety
OL,17,Fnet' population at Jersey Zoo to stop
OL,18,Fthem from becoming extinct.
